{
  "stem": "7781.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But after school, I was kind of-- I felt, oh, well, brothers are working, and I-- and I was glad they let me do something, because they didn't trust me doing more.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They let me do menial things, like sweep the floor and those things.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But otherwise, you know, they didn't make me work.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Till-- till I finished school, then I started to learn the trade.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, there was-- it was four stories high, four story.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we had-- we lived on the-- I would say on the third floor.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the first floor, my father had the shop.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the second floor was a synagogue, a little synagogue.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And-- and the-- and the top floor, there were, I guess, two families lived.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They were poor people, mostly.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They worked in the same room, and they lived in the same room, and everything was done in one room.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So compared to them, we had separate, so we were better off.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The time about-- about-- before the war, if I look back, mainly I think about the family and the neighbors and the Jewish life.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And-- and-- and I think a lot about it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it's [INAUDIBLE] I live it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I remember neighbors, in all those years.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I remember name.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Everything has gone out, a world disappeared.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "When I when back to Poland, to, you know, take my daughter and show her where we lived, it was a very sad experience, you know, to look at the building.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And from all the people that lived there in that building, and there were children, and nobody was left for me to say hello.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So a whole world disappeared.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It just disappeared.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it-- and this makes me very, very sad.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I cannot stop thinking about it.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
